Display Max Capacity message

Program Check Availability button
  Compare #ofGuests to #bedsAvailable
    Display success/fail message

Program Make Reservation Button
  Compare #Guests to #bedsAvailable
    Display fail message/ make reservation

Make Reservation
  Calculate beds needed
  Subtract beds needed from Total Beds
  Display message
    Success, Rooms Booked, Rooms Available

Function
  compare Guests with Beds ==> yes/no
  display fail message

