Check Availability
-input # of guests
-calculate # of rooms needed
-compare to rooms available
  -yes/no
  -display appropriate message

Make Reservation
-Check available
  -yes/no
  -if no - display appropriate message
  -if yes - make the reservation
    -remove rooms
    -display new totals 
